{"tid":946892,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"個個星期都嗌交","createTime":"2018-12-19T00:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T03:43:22.000Z","uid":194403,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"129064c78d5c8638d19880f160fbfa176112e9b2","tid":946892,"uid":194403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T00:52:34.000Z","msg":"只係想呻下，拍拖兩年幾，基本上近幾個月開始經常嗌交<br />\n<br />\n例如公司趕出貨，要我幫手聖誕有開一日工，聖誕後補返日假，一講完就怪我聖誕無得見，唔諗下幾時同佢食聖誕餐等等，又嗌過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實有諗，打算聖誕前後去食，有一路say sorry，但可惜佢已經聽唔入耳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n坦白講我聖誕要開工已經好灰，宜家嗌埋交仲灰"},{"pid":"57df15124b848481e3e2931a0951ea60b7df1db6","tid":946892,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T00:55:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c7939f0d9996f2c8599abee32df88bbdefbc4c8","tid":946892,"uid":84954,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:10:34.000Z","msg":"好後生?<br />\n唔係份份工都朝9晚5架喎<br />\n識著個輪班既咁點?<br />\n何況做服務業大時大節就係搵錢時間<br />\n咁都唔識諗就飛撚左佢啦"},{"pid":"fd26c60b6a65ee610b134785df77833eaf9d389f","tid":946892,"uid":157579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57df15124b848481e3e2931a0951ea60b7df1db6","tid":946892,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T00:55:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:11:29.000Z","msg":"X1<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a97eb2ebe944cebfe0e3d6b8a332b181729bd9b","tid":946892,"uid":201834,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a315f9382bc9a83da1440755151df92ab1611c27","tid":946892,"uid":194403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a97eb2ebe944cebfe0e3d6b8a332b181729bd9b","tid":946892,"uid":201834,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:14:08.000Z","msg":"